<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Nichengin Ei Sam Ie !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa'n A hehpihte gam A guotsak chu,
 Khawvel Kanaan gam sanga le nuomzaw chu,
 A aw nemin a mite nicheng in ei sam
 A gam nuom taka chun cheng dingin.

[V2]
 Ni chengin ei sam ie,
 A aw nem ngai un
 A hehpihna hun zuon un, hun zuon un.
 Jordan luipi lien mah leh,
 Lalpa gama chun hung lut tei un.

[V3]
 2. Aw, ziechun Hinna Thing leh lenthang khawvui
 Thilin ka ngai hinna pakcha lun lai chu,
 Thienna luipang hawih leh kumsawt hinna mun nuom
 Lalpa lungsiet te laituol lenna.

[V4]
 3. Aw, ziechun kumsawt a eng Lalpa Isu,
 Leh Angelte tawh kipahna la sai tiu;
 Krista mel ente chun gitlohna lau loin,
 Lawpin Amah chu a chawian ui.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>188</hymn_number>
<author>Chhawna</author>
</song>